metadata.name: Empress Trash - Computer Love
metadata.description:
Part of the Vintage Glitch series, made for SuperChief x NFTRome Bad Glitches Only exhibition.
4k .mp4 animated loop created with AI, Photomosh and After Effects.

Computer Love is a portrait of how technology brings us closer together while causing a disconnect at the same time. Are we really intimate with each other or the tech around us?
